ng></i><br><i>&quot;Cross through the hardship, To the saloon.&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/27e6d541cd1e441c3c7ba9d43ef6b34d.poster.avif?t=1727363104\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/27e6d541cd1e441c3c7ba9d43ef6b34d.webm?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/27e6d541cd1e441c3c7ba9d43ef6b34d.mp4?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot;More whiskey, More ability&quot;</strong></i><br><i>&quot;A proper drinking makes you stronger. Only in game.&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/551ca5933bba8c993c9628c0495f7f9c.poster.avif?t=1727363104\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/551ca5933bba8c993c9628c0495f7f9c.webm?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/551ca5933bba8c993c9628c0495f7f9c.mp4?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot;Weapon upgrade for more quick punishment&quot;</strong></i><br><i>&quot;An improved trigger can be pulled much powerful, and the bullet getting stronger. (No)&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/a0ed5ddf64ed2cfccbab726d074b82fe.poster.avif?t=1727363104\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/a0ed5ddf64ed2cfccbab726d074b82fe.webm?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165040/extras/a0ed5ddf64ed2cfccbab726d074b82fe.mp4?t=1727363104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot;Finally realized justice for boss&quot;</strong></i><br><i>&quot;My bullet will pass trough the evil's heart, At last it goes to my future.&quot;</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Information</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight alone against bandits rushing in!<br></li><li>It consists of total 20 waves and the boss appears in each 5 wave.<br></li><li>You can select an ability after clear the wave.<br></li><li>After wave end, moving to saloon. You can use the credits to buy ability, upgrade the weapons and recover the health<br></li><li>Through the lantern in saloon to progress the next wave.<br></li><li>Get the victory by clear the final wave!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mouse Left Button - Fire<br></li><li>Mouse Right Button or &quot;R&quot; - Reload<br></li><li>Mouse Wheel or &quot;1,2,3,4&quot; - Switching Weapon<br></li><li>&quot;ESC&quot; - Game Pause or Resume<br></li><li>&quot;`&quot; - Console Open or Close (Can use after clear the Lawless Area)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Release Version Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More Abilities - More than twice as many abilities are available compared to the demo version.<br></li><li>Pump Shotgun - New weapon &quot;Pump Shotgun&quot; and related abilities are available in saloon.<br></li><li>Lawless Area Difiiculty - A challenging difficulty that has more powerful and various enemies, and getting disadvantageous penalties. (Available after clear the Daily Life Difficulty)<br></li><li>Reputation System - More the playing the game, more additional features unlocked.<br></li><li>Achievement - Recording monumental achievements.<br></li><li>Console Command - Can use the cheats! (Refer to online manual, Can't progress reputation and achievement if used, Available after clear the Lawless Area Difficulty)</li></ul>",
